/**
 * @module GAI — Master AI Engine v3.0
 * @description The single AI brain of Atassa-MD.
 *   • Natural language intent routing (music, video, weather, lyrics, QR, screenshot, define, npm, translate...)
 *   • Gem persona system (SQLite-backed, persistent)
 *   • Auto-reply engine (DM mode, chat mode, target mode, global stalk mode)
 *   • Image generation via Infip (15+ models, chaos/surprise/enhance)
 *   • Dynamic WhatsApp profile (AI name/bio/pfp)
 *   • Circuit-breaker + rate-limiter + full fallback chain
 *   • All responses are EDITED in-place (no spam)
 *   • Quoted messages (text + images) passed to AI context
 * @note Built for Atassa Bulletproof Framework (gifted-baileys).
 *       Exact same AI/image APIs as Python counterpart; JS port by Claude.
 */

